# Images Directory

Place your images here:

## Structure

```
images/
├── avatar.jpg           # Your profile picture
├── og-image.png         # Open Graph image for social sharing
├── blog/                # Blog post images
│   ├── nextjs-14.jpg
│   └── ...
└── projects/            # Project screenshots
    ├── ecommerce.jpg
    ├── taskapp.jpg
    └── ...
```

## Image Guidelines

- Use optimized images (WebP or JPEG)
- Recommended sizes:
  - Avatar: 200x200px
  - OG Image: 1200x630px
  - Blog Headers: 1200x600px
  - Project Screenshots: 1200x800px

- Keep file sizes under 200KB when possible
- Use descriptive filenames
